The paper discusses the challenges posed by Big Data for the social sciences, particularly in terms of analyzing and understanding the vast amounts of data generated by digital networks. This suggests that the paper is likely to fall under the category of Social and Information Retrieval (cs.SI), which deals with the analysis of social media and other online platforms. Additionally, the paper touches on issues related to cybersecurity (cs.CY), data mining (cs.SD), cryptography (cs.CR), and information retrieval (cs.IR), all of which are relevant to the challenges posed by Big Data.
